item.content:encoded:
Hello there!

My name is Ola and I am currently a third year Digital Media student in the Institute of Technology Blanchardstown. I have a huge interest in photography, design, both graphic and web and also magazine layouts and film.

I have a very good knowledge of the Adobe Suite but mainly Dreamweaver, Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign and Premiere Pro. I can also use Reaper and Wordpress.

I speak few languages, Polish (native), English and French (beginners). But I also know the language of html, css, javascript and php.

item.title: PHOTOGRAPHY
item.dc:creator: oluusieq
item.content:encoded:
I have a huge passion for photography. I started my adventure with it when I was 15. I use photography to escape the real world and create an imaginary world where for a minute everything is perfect. My main area of focus is portraits. I love to portray the emotions, freeze a moment and enjoy what we have now because it might be gone within seconds.

Visit my facebook page for more photos: www.facebook.com/simplecreationsphoto/

item.title: BRANDING
item.dc:creator: oluusieq
item.content:encoded:
Branding is an area of design that I would like to work in the most. I like the problem solving and helping companies get recognised. I have a great eye for detail and great knowledge of the colour psychology.
  Some of my work: Ctone is an online hearing test company. They are a start up and asked a group of college students to create a brand for their company. This project included creating a logo design, business card, compliment slip, an app icon and an app loading screen. Master logo Business Cards, front and back App loading screen and stationary  
Babel is a newly opened English School. The client originally wanted a website for his company only but after few talks and suggestions he agreed to brand the whole company. This project is still in process. Master logo Website home page mock-up
Just Paint is a painting and decorating company. The client wanted a logo for his business and now he asked to develop a simple website which is under construction. Master logo Website www.justpaint.ie

item.title: VIDEO PRODUCTION
item.dc:creator: oluusieq
item.content:encoded:
My adventure with video began few years ago. The first film I created was for a competition. In college, we have a big emphasis on video production and post-production. I know the technical as well as practical aspects of film. To me, film is much like photography but it's a set of moving photos. The same rules apply to both. I particularly like the editing part of filming. I like to create something out of nothing. And get the audience to feel for the character, which is a huge challenge.

Stamped Rough Cut

As part of our third year Drama Filmmaking we have to produce a short film. Synopsis of the film: James had a falling out with his family. They haven’t spoken in years. When James finds out that his father is dying he decides to visit him. His sister gives him an ultimatum to collect the stamp his father has been searching for years or she won’t speak to him again. James swallows his pride and sets out on this journey where he encounters a lot of difficulties. He is forced to do things out of his comfort zone. Travels around Ireland hopelessly. When his hope of finding the stamp dies, he sets back home, just to find out that the hope hasn’t fully died yet. My role in this project is to be a director, and video editor. https://vimeo.com/195214697

The Streets of Culture Documentary

As part of our second year filming module, in groups we had to make a documentary. My colleague and I decided to do our documentary on busking in Dublin and the bye laws that are currently in place. I was the director of photography as well as an editor.

https://vimeo.com/193338418  

Redub Assignment

A quick redub assignment for our third year Sound Design module. https://vimeo.com/190789930  

Music Video

Also, in second year filming module we had to create a music video for a song of our choice. I chose the song 'The Beach' by The Neighbourhood because I really wanted to create a black and white music video. I was inspired by their previous videos.

https://vimeo.com/150496571  

Silent Short Film

This is the first film I ever created. It was for a James Bay competition. It tells a story of a girl going through a break up. The film was one of the top most liked films in the competition.
